node.text: Fabulous mountain estate 30 minutes from Denver that boasts spectacular views of the mountains. Set on an acre of wooded serenity this home has 10k sqft of impeccably finished space including 6 bedrooms and 9 bathrooms. The main floor master walks out to the resort style pool and massive entertaining area. Above the over-sized four car garage is a mother in law suite that you have to see!  The walk out to the front basement is full of surprises including a sunken theatre and a hidden man cave for your entertaining delight. This home is your dream come true and will not disappoint! Priced at $4,000,000. via @shauncaseyrealestate

node.text:
Listed for $87,777,777 - A premiere new Bel-Air estate, 777 Sarbonne Road is an ultra-luxe, architectural masterpiece, offering unparalleled views, scale, and amenities for futural living on over an acre. 

Previously owned by Alex Khadavi, a world-renowned celebrity cosmetic and reconstructive surgeon, Palazzo di Vista features arguably one of the greatest views of Los Angeles––stretching from the San Gabriel Mountains to Palos Verdes, Downtown Los Angeles, Santa Monica, Malibu, and The Channel Islands. Khadavi began designing and building the palatial masterpiece in 2016, inspired by Italian mathematician Fibonacci’s way of thinking. 

Palazzo di Vista represents all elements of life while encompassing Fibonacci’s Golden Ratio. Between the main home and the guest house, the estate boasts seven bedrooms, eleven bathrooms, a multi-million dollar curated art collection, exquisite design and spectacular, contemporary living.

Credit to (@theultimatedesign)

node.text:
Home of the Day! Courtesy of @dezerplatinumrealty & @liv_mor 

Location: Sunny Isles Beach, Florida
Price: $21,000,000
Living Area: 8,407 sq ft
Beds: 5
Baths: 7

Maximize this unique one of a kind opportunity to combine 2 apartments at the Porsche Design Tower. The potential of these two combined apartments is a living space of almost 7,000 sq. ft. and interior parking for 4 cars. 

Current bedroom configuration stands at 5 bedrooms with an expanded entertainment area. Because it has 2 floors, the potential for combinations is almost limitless. You can access the second bedroom from the top, through the floor, or rearrange the bedrooms any way you wish and really make the most out of this wonderful viewing space. 

Expansive floor to ceiling windows showcase the breathtaking sunset and city views. Porsche Design Tower is known worldwide for its exclusivity and privacy, being the only building that allows you to ride up in your car into your home.

Listed for €17,500,000 - Palatial, newly built, uniquely luxurious, state of the art villa with 1100 m² living space and extensive landscaped grounds. It has a 100m frontage onto the Vinkeveense lake (Plassen) and a 40m long private sandy beach. The villa has been developed with close attention to the smallest details.
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Very private and serene location where between high evergreen hedges, two double electric doors (in&out) connect the quiet road with the wide driveway. The +100m Vinkeveense Plassen water frontage has 3 integrated jetty terraces directly over the water. There are extensive mooring facilities.Continuing along the lake from the over water terraces and boat mooring frontage is a private 40 meters long white sandy beach. The Beach house has showers, bathrooms a BBQ and a bar with cooking facilities.

Credit to (@mega_mansions)
